Imprisoner/Predator/Choran:




Imprisoner laughed as Savanna fell, and walked over to Spitfire's body.

Predator got up.  "HA!  DIE STUPID MAXIMAL!" he screamed, mech-fluid seaping 
out of his face and hands from numerous cuts made by Savanna.  Raising his 
grenade launcher, he fired off a grenade at Savanna's head, smiling wickedly.

Imprisoner began stomping on Spitfire's head.  
"I--told---you---not---to--follow--us.  
You--should--of---listened---stupid--Maximal!"

Choran walked over to the overturned Hot Rod, who was still in his vehicle 
mode.  Raising his rifle, he fired off two shots, one at the front left 
tire's, and the other at the back right tire.
